1
00:00:47,650 --> 00:00:48,449
Zhou Yimo...

2
00:00:49,250 --> 00:00:50,609
I am your step mother.

3
00:01:27,130 --> 00:01:28,849
You care about me,

4
00:01:29,210 --> 00:01:30,169
don't you?

5
00:02:18,730 --> 00:02:22,729
[Zhou's residence]

6
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:02,800
Episode 1

7
00:03:10,850 --> 00:03:12,569
The Zhou manor is haunted.

8
00:03:12,690 --> 00:03:14,289
The master fell ill.

9
00:03:14,290 --> 00:03:15,649
Your life force is vigorous.

10
00:03:15,890 --> 00:03:17,569
Master Zhou took you as his fifth concubine

11
00:03:17,570 --> 00:03:19,209
to ward off evil spirits.

12
00:03:19,290 --> 00:03:20,729
And yet, this is a position

13
00:03:20,810 --> 00:03:23,649
many covet but few attain.

14
00:03:26,770 --> 00:03:28,369
Once I join the Zhou family,

15
00:03:29,250 --> 00:03:30,289
I am the ghost.

16
00:03:31,170 --> 00:03:32,609
I am the evil spirit.

17
00:03:44,930 --> 00:03:46,089
Three years ago,

18
00:03:46,490 --> 00:03:48,049
my sister Ye Chuxue

19
00:03:48,050 --> 00:03:49,529
worked as a maid at Zhou manor.

20
00:03:49,930 --> 00:03:51,969
After suffering inhuman abuse,

21
00:03:51,290 --> 00:03:54,085
[Ye Chuxue, a maid at Zhou manor]

22
00:03:51,970 --> 00:03:53,329
she died mysteriously.

23
00:03:53,450 --> 00:03:55,729
The Zhou family and police covered the truth,

24
00:03:55,890 --> 00:03:57,849
closing the case as suicide by drowning.

25
00:03:58,010 --> 00:04:00,009
I will make everyone who hurt my sister

26
00:04:00,290 --> 00:04:02,689
pay the price they deserve.

27
00:04:11,210 --> 00:04:13,089
I wondered where this floral scent came from.

28
00:04:13,450 --> 00:04:15,889
So it's the new fifth concubine.

29
00:04:19,090 --> 00:04:20,689
[Ye Zhiqiu, fifth concubine]

30
00:04:20,730 --> 00:04:23,569
[Zhou Yimo, the eldest son of the Zhou family]

31
00:04:27,930 --> 00:04:28,689
Greetings, Young Master.

32
00:04:30,810 --> 00:04:31,849
Have you seen me before?

33
00:04:32,890 --> 00:04:34,329
The first young master is wild at heart

34
00:04:34,650 --> 00:04:35,689
and adrift in the world.

35
00:04:36,130 --> 00:04:37,569
The second young master is a gentle

36
00:04:37,890 --> 00:04:38,929
and refined gentleman.

37
00:04:39,850 --> 00:04:41,089
With your demeanor,

38
00:04:42,130 --> 00:04:42,969
you must be the first young master.

39
00:04:44,690 --> 00:04:46,129
You're quite flattering.

40
00:04:48,890 --> 00:04:50,289
Would you like me to take

41
00:04:50,530 --> 00:04:51,409
these damn shackles off for you?

42
00:04:51,970 --> 00:04:52,409
Young Master,

43
00:04:52,850 --> 00:04:53,529
it's for warding off evil spirits.

44
00:04:53,890 --> 00:04:54,329
You can't.

45
00:04:58,890 --> 00:04:59,849
Brother, do not be rude.

46
00:05:04,010 --> 00:05:05,209
Zhou Yichen, the Second Young Master

47
00:05:05,370 --> 00:05:08,129
and heir apparent to the Zhou family.

48
00:05:06,677 --> 00:05:09,049
[Zhou Yichen, Second Young Master]

49
00:05:14,770 --> 00:05:15,809
Greetings, Second Young Master.

50
00:05:19,290 --> 00:05:20,489
Fifth Concubine, you recognize me?

51
00:05:20,650 --> 00:05:22,049
She has already researched

52
00:05:22,050 --> 00:05:22,769
both of us brothers.

53
00:05:22,810 --> 00:05:23,409
Elder brother,

54
00:05:24,130 --> 00:05:25,089
do not be rude.

55
00:05:26,330 --> 00:05:27,129
Fifth Concubine,

56
00:05:27,330 --> 00:05:28,249
this is my elder brother.

57
00:05:28,570 --> 00:05:29,849
He lives by his own rules.

58
00:05:30,090 --> 00:05:30,929
Please forgive him.

59
00:05:31,410 --> 00:05:32,289
Father is occupied at the moment.

60
00:05:32,770 --> 00:05:33,529
I'll take you there.

61
00:05:33,890 --> 00:05:34,729
Thank you, Second Young Master.

62
00:06:03,930 --> 00:06:05,849
This is the price of betraying me.

63
00:06:07,850 --> 00:06:09,129
Please wait a moment.

64
00:06:20,090 --> 00:06:20,929
Steward,

65
00:06:21,570 --> 00:06:22,649
clean this up immediately.

66
00:06:22,690 --> 00:06:23,449
Yes!

67
00:06:26,610 --> 00:06:27,449
Father,

68
00:06:28,170 --> 00:06:29,449
it's time for your wedding ceremony.

69
00:06:29,770 --> 00:06:31,849
[Zhou Huaiqian, Master of the Zhou family]

70
00:06:31,850 --> 00:06:32,649
Let's go.

71
00:06:40,250 --> 00:06:41,809
Auspicious clouds surround the house,

72
00:06:42,090 --> 00:06:44,169
joy fills the courtyard.

73
00:06:44,530 --> 00:06:46,609
Today Zhou manor welcomes new blood.

74
00:06:46,770 --> 00:06:48,849
Our master is in his prime,

75
00:06:49,290 --> 00:06:50,209
now taking.

76
00:06:50,210 --> 00:06:51,569
his fifth concubine.

77
00:06:52,170 --> 00:06:53,009
First bow

78
00:06:53,170 --> 00:06:54,809
to Tea Mountain spring scenery,

79
00:06:54,810 --> 00:06:57,369
favorable weather for abundant harvest.

80
00:06:58,050 --> 00:06:58,969
Second bow

81
00:06:58,970 --> 00:07:00,329
to Zhou family ancestors.

82
00:07:11,690 --> 00:07:12,409
[Xu Hansheng, Steward]
Three bows...

83
00:07:12,410 --> 00:07:13,609
Where did all these bats come from?

84
00:07:12,420 --> 00:07:12,748
[Xu Hansheng, Steward]

85
00:07:16,330 --> 00:07:17,009
Bats!

86
00:07:17,770 --> 00:07:18,089
Quick!

87
00:07:18,250 --> 00:07:18,689
Get torches!

88
00:07:18,690 --> 00:07:19,129
Yes!

89
00:07:21,370 --> 00:07:22,329
Master Zhou, be careful!

90
00:07:27,570 --> 00:07:28,049
Hurry!

91
00:07:28,050 --> 00:07:28,689
Someone help!

92
00:07:44,490 --> 00:07:44,929
Master Zhou,

93
00:07:45,250 --> 00:07:46,009
are you alright?

94
00:07:47,250 --> 00:07:47,929
I'm fine.

95
00:07:51,530 --> 00:07:52,249
You're injured.

96
00:07:52,610 --> 00:07:53,569
As long as you're unharmed...

97
00:07:53,930 --> 00:07:54,809
I'm not seriously hurt.

98
00:08:19,970 --> 00:08:21,529
You're not afraid of bats?

99
00:08:22,530 --> 00:08:23,569
Afraid of me?

100
00:08:24,650 --> 00:08:25,929
I'm not afraid.

101
00:08:31,770 --> 00:08:32,849
Does your hand still hurt?

102
00:08:36,050 --> 00:08:37,089
Not anymore.

103
00:08:58,650 --> 00:09:00,729
Wasn't Master Zhou critically ill?

104
00:09:00,890 --> 00:09:01,609
How could...

105
00:09:03,210 --> 00:09:04,169
Master Zhou, you...

106
00:09:04,170 --> 00:09:05,889
Since you've married me,

107
00:09:06,290 --> 00:09:07,689
don't have regrets.

108
00:09:27,490 --> 00:09:28,569
What are you doing?

109
00:09:31,490 --> 00:09:33,529
Eavesdropping on dad?

110
00:09:35,730 --> 00:09:36,489
Just passing by.

111
00:09:37,730 --> 00:09:38,849
And I wanted to ask about his health.

112
00:09:38,850 --> 00:09:39,689
What?

113
00:09:41,090 --> 00:09:42,209
You know perfectly well

114
00:09:42,490 --> 00:09:44,369
over the years, dad's... performance

115
00:09:45,210 --> 00:09:46,209
has indeed

116
00:09:46,890 --> 00:09:47,489
been lacking.

117
00:09:47,610 --> 00:09:47,969
Elder brother!

118
00:09:47,970 --> 00:09:48,969
If you put it that way,

119
00:09:50,250 --> 00:09:51,249
you're just provoking him.

120
00:09:52,090 --> 00:09:53,169
You're so bold that you dare

121
00:09:53,970 --> 00:09:55,089
gossip about Father behind his back.

122
00:09:56,730 --> 00:09:57,769
You are

123
00:09:58,730 --> 00:10:00,089
a perfect gentleman,

124
00:10:00,810 --> 00:10:02,809
the apple of his eye...

125
00:10:03,090 --> 00:10:04,209
Stop being sarcastic.

126
00:10:05,210 --> 00:10:06,609
Where were you

127
00:10:08,090 --> 00:10:08,769
when father needed you most?

128
00:10:45,130 --> 00:10:46,129
Congratulations, Fifth Concubine.

129
00:10:46,610 --> 00:10:47,369
This is

130
00:10:47,370 --> 00:10:49,209
Master's recognition and "welcome gift."

131
00:10:49,450 --> 00:10:50,849
The master treats all his wives well.

132
00:10:50,970 --> 00:10:52,129
You'll see in time.

133
00:10:54,210 --> 00:10:55,089
Thank you, steward.

134
00:10:55,490 --> 00:10:56,329
I'll return alone.

135
00:10:56,930 --> 00:10:57,609
Please stay here.

136
00:10:57,810 --> 00:10:58,129
Alright.

137
00:11:07,730 --> 00:11:08,889
No matter what,

138
00:11:09,090 --> 00:11:10,529
I've finally stayed.

139
00:11:18,130 --> 00:11:19,289
The Zhou family reports

140
00:11:19,850 --> 00:11:22,409
Ye Chuxue's body was found in the mansion pond.

141
00:11:23,290 --> 00:11:24,449
The deceased's body

142
00:11:24,850 --> 00:11:26,329
bears a total of 137

143
00:11:26,330 --> 00:11:27,809
cigarette burn marks.

144
00:11:29,490 --> 00:11:30,249
Next,

145
00:11:31,250 --> 00:11:32,289
it's time to meet the first

146
00:11:32,290 --> 00:11:33,729
suspect in my sister's murder.

147
00:11:37,130 --> 00:11:41,049
[He Wangshu, second concubine]

148
00:11:49,850 --> 00:11:50,369
Talk!

149
00:11:51,170 --> 00:11:52,849
Who tampered with the food box?

150
00:11:53,290 --> 00:11:54,009
Second Concubine,

151
00:11:54,210 --> 00:11:55,489
I truly don't know.

152
00:11:57,770 --> 00:11:59,689
[Lan'er, maid]

153
00:11:59,690 --> 00:12:00,609
Seems

154
00:12:01,690 --> 00:12:02,929
you're itching for punishment.

155
00:12:06,490 --> 00:12:07,169
Second concubine,

156
00:12:09,770 --> 00:12:10,969
I delivered the food box.

157
00:12:10,335 --> 00:12:13,677
[Zhang Nanxi, head maid]

158
00:12:11,210 --> 00:12:12,849
You and the new Fifth Concubine

159
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:13,865
each received one.

160
00:12:13,890 --> 00:12:16,049
A poor jinxed scapegoat—

161
00:12:16,170 --> 00:12:16,929
how dare she!

162
00:12:17,210 --> 00:12:18,329
I'm just a maid.

163
00:12:18,730 --> 00:12:19,969
I dare not discuss concubine's affairs.

164
00:12:21,090 --> 00:12:22,369
If you have concerns,

165
00:12:22,730 --> 00:12:23,929
you should ask the Master directly.

166
00:12:27,730 --> 00:12:29,009
Then tell me,

167
00:12:29,370 --> 00:12:31,529
why did this appear in the food box

168
00:12:32,650 --> 00:12:34,009
from the kitchen?

169
00:12:34,170 --> 00:12:36,089
I carried the box myself the whole way.

170
00:12:36,170 --> 00:12:37,089
No one touched it.

171
00:12:37,610 --> 00:12:38,329
I don't know.

172
00:12:38,730 --> 00:12:39,529
Get out!

173
00:12:42,730 --> 00:12:43,329
Go!

174
00:12:49,210 --> 00:12:51,449
I know what you did back then.

175
00:12:52,210 --> 00:12:53,089
Tonight,

176
00:12:53,410 --> 00:12:55,329
come find me at the backyard pond.

177
00:13:16,290 --> 00:13:17,529
Why did you ask me here?

178
00:13:19,330 --> 00:13:19,929
Who are you?

179
00:13:44,290 --> 00:13:45,369
Looks like Zhou Manor has more than

180
00:13:45,570 --> 00:13:46,769
one ghost stirring the shadows.

181
00:13:47,690 --> 00:13:49,249
I wronged you.

182
00:13:50,730 --> 00:13:51,769
Spare me.

183
00:13:51,770 --> 00:13:53,049
I know I was wrong.

184
00:13:53,810 --> 00:13:54,729
A ghost!

185
00:13:55,170 --> 00:13:55,929
Help!

186
00:13:56,210 --> 00:13:57,169
I don't want to die!

187
00:13:58,130 --> 00:13:58,889
Second concubine, what's wrong?

188
00:13:58,890 --> 00:13:59,729
A ghost!

189
00:14:00,050 --> 00:14:00,609
Second concubine!

190
00:14:00,610 --> 00:14:01,369
Are you alright?

191
00:14:01,370 --> 00:14:04,049
She tried to drown me!

192
00:14:05,730 --> 00:14:06,449
There's a ghost!

193
00:14:06,930 --> 00:14:07,649
A ghost!

194
00:14:12,330 --> 00:14:12,769
Where is she?

195
00:14:13,570 --> 00:14:14,129
Steward,

196
00:14:14,330 --> 00:14:15,289
there's a water trail over the corridor.

197
00:14:15,930 --> 00:14:16,689
Take the second concubine back.

198
00:14:16,690 --> 00:14:17,129
Yes.

199
00:14:17,130 --> 00:14:18,049
Gather all the servants!

200
00:14:18,050 --> 00:14:18,569
Search everywhere!

201
00:14:18,570 --> 00:14:19,289
Yes.

202
00:14:21,530 --> 00:14:22,249
Over here!

203
00:14:22,250 --> 00:14:22,489
After her!

204
00:14:22,530 --> 00:14:22,929
Follow me!

205
00:14:24,890 --> 00:14:26,129
Search carefully here too.

206
00:14:26,210 --> 00:14:27,249
Got it.
- Yes!

207
00:14:27,450 --> 00:14:28,169
Freeze!

208
00:14:52,090 --> 00:14:52,769
This way.

209
00:14:52,810 --> 00:14:54,009
Search carefully.

210
00:15:08,810 --> 00:15:09,809
Why did you bite me?

211
00:15:10,930 --> 00:15:12,489
What are you doing here in the middle of the night?

212
00:15:12,490 --> 00:15:13,769
I came when I heard shouting.

213
00:15:13,770 --> 00:15:14,849
What a coincidence!

214
00:15:15,170 --> 00:15:16,169
I should be asking you

215
00:15:17,410 --> 00:15:19,849
why are you here on your wedding night?

216
00:15:19,970 --> 00:15:21,809
Do I need your permission?

217
00:15:21,850 --> 00:15:22,969
On your first day here,

218
00:15:23,170 --> 00:15:24,289
wandering around the backyard

219
00:15:24,850 --> 00:15:25,929
it's hard not to suspect

220
00:15:26,050 --> 00:15:27,969
you came here with ulterior motives.

221
00:15:27,970 --> 00:15:29,169
I lost something important.

222
00:15:29,530 --> 00:15:30,609
I got lost while searching.

223
00:15:31,090 --> 00:15:31,809
Young Master,

224
00:15:32,170 --> 00:15:33,369
I'm your dad's concubine.

225
00:15:33,970 --> 00:15:34,969
Show some respect.

226
00:15:37,010 --> 00:15:38,529
Are you looking for this?

227
00:15:52,690 --> 00:15:53,369
Where did you find it?

228
00:15:54,690 --> 00:15:55,929
How will you repay me?

229
00:15:56,570 --> 00:15:57,489
I'll think about it.

230
00:16:10,490 --> 00:16:11,769
Just help me put it on.

231
00:16:12,570 --> 00:16:14,489
Anything goes.

232
00:16:17,330 --> 00:16:18,809
Would you like to see

233
00:16:20,050 --> 00:16:23,169
the tattoo your father inked on me?

234
00:16:27,250 --> 00:16:29,369
I've no interest in his vulgar tastes.

235
00:16:36,890 --> 00:16:38,489
But I am intrigued by you.

236
00:16:43,450 --> 00:16:44,929
Release me! You're choking me!

237
00:16:44,930 --> 00:16:45,569
Speak!

238
00:16:46,130 --> 00:16:47,449
Where did this jade pendant come from?

239
00:16:48,050 --> 00:16:50,449
Cheap jade trinkets litter every street.

240
00:16:50,810 --> 00:16:52,329
Why would you care so much?

241
00:16:54,010 --> 00:16:56,129
If you don't tell me the truth, this rope will only tighten.

242
00:16:56,130 --> 00:16:57,889
I ask you one last time

243
00:16:58,250 --> 00:16:59,889
where is the jade pendant from?

244
00:17:00,250 --> 00:17:01,369
Who exactly are you?

245
00:17:06,810 --> 00:17:07,929
Who else could I be?

246
00:17:09,370 --> 00:17:10,409
I'm your father's

247
00:17:11,370 --> 00:17:13,129
new concubine.

248
00:17:14,010 --> 00:17:14,769
Is that so?

249
00:17:29,010 --> 00:17:30,089
Let's just forget

250
00:17:30,090 --> 00:17:31,249
what happened tonight.

251
00:17:31,690 --> 00:17:32,609
I never saw you,

252
00:17:33,210 --> 00:17:34,249
you never saw me.

253
00:17:38,570 --> 00:17:40,569
You're quite ruthless.

254
00:17:41,210 --> 00:17:42,649
I'll be crueler toward

255
00:17:42,650 --> 00:17:43,569
those who threaten me.

256
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:46,809
You'd best keep your distance.

257
00:17:53,530 --> 00:17:54,689
Just as I thought it's her.
